    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/1602c50713894a2bb1d11c396107822a.avif?t=1772124595\" width=600 height=143 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle Vision! The intergalactic sensation is back for its 12 billionth smash season! Challenge enemies from throughout the galaxy as you lead your team through thrilling tournament runs filled with sweet victory and bitter defeat. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/40344e6c757b466facf77a9b3f0236b9.avif?t=1772124595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras_big/40344e6c757b466facf77a9b3f0236b9.webp?t=1772124595 width=1560 height=72 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create attacks by color-matching units. Launch them into the enemy’s endzone to score points! Vertical matches create attackers, horizontal ones defenses. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is simple and satisfying to jump into. Endless depth of strategy emerges with advanced play. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/993dbefa2c9bf2ac1ef0236aa0c7915d.poster.avif?t=1772124595\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/993dbefa2c9bf2ac1ef0236aa0c7915d.webm?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/993dbefa2c9bf2ac1ef0236aa0c7915d.mp4?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/7cd726749d667433205dd6da76235a45.avif?t=1772124595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras_big/7cd726749d667433205dd6da76235a45.webp?t=1772124595 width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your battles carefully on the branching path through the tournament season.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some routes have higher difficulty, along with greater rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/00287ef23ee70f880bb1bbc8b56c791e.poster.avif?t=1772124595\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/00287ef23ee70f880bb1bbc8b56c791e.webm?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/00287ef23ee70f880bb1bbc8b56c791e.mp4?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/125f22fa15d3d6733dbc3c91cd3b3d90.avif?t=1772124595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras_big/125f22fa15d3d6733dbc3c91cd3b3d90.webp?t=1772124595 width=1560 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humble beginnings provide limited teams and units to choose from - but options expand as you play, whether you win or lose. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Win Bux as you progress and spend them on new unit types, Performance Enhancement upgrades, and more game-changing items to give you an edge in battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/ff75f96a91315da7d19976f1947f8128.poster.avif?t=1772124595\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/ff75f96a91315da7d19976f1947f8128.webm?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/ff75f96a91315da7d19976f1947f8128.mp4?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/1ebf5c71616adaba326ad1599a995eea.avif?t=1772124595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras_big/1ebf5c71616adaba326ad1599a995eea.webp?t=1772124595 width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover novel synergies between captains, units, and upgrades to change the tides of battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Masterfully combine of unit special effects, captain abilities, performance enhancements, and consumable items to create devastating team attacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter surprising enemy abilities as you advance in your campaign.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/78e1bf2198292ea48ba38751aa284215.poster.avif?t=1772124595\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/78e1bf2198292ea48ba38751aa284215.webm?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2216850/extras/78e1bf2198292ea48ba38751aa284215.mp4?t=1772124595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
